        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div id="rain-info" class="tree-info">
        <div class="tree-header">
            <div class="tree-icon">‚òî</div>
            <h3>Rain Tree</h3>
        </div>
        <p>The Rain tree has a clever way to spread its seeds!</p>
        
        <div class="tree-details">
            <div class="detail-card">
