    <h2>Why is Seed Dispersal Important?</h2>
    <div style="background-color: #f1f8e9; padding: 20px; border-radius: 15px; margin: 20px 0;">
        <p style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><span class="seed-icon">‚úÖ</span> Reduces competition for water and sunlight.</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><span class="seed-icon">‚úÖ</span> Helps plants grow in new places.</p>
        <p><span class="seed-icon">‚úÖ</span> Makes sure plants don't all grow in one spot.</p>
    </div>
    
