        </div>
        <ul class="fact-list">
            <li>The coco-de-mer seed can weigh up to 18 kg (like a 4-year-old child!) and floats in the ocean.</li>
            <li>Some seeds can travel over 10,000 km by ocean currents.</li>
            <li>Burdock seeds inspired the invention of VELCRO¬Æ because they stick so well!</li>
        </ul>
